<p>We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide when using our website.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Personal details (name, email address, etc.)</li>
    <li>Meal preferences, likes, dislikes, allergies (if applicable)</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>The information we collect could be used to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Provide personalized meal planning suggestions</li>
    <li>Improve our website and services</li>
